data.text:
Go Fish

Xander goes undercover as a swimmer to help Buffy net a sea monster that's been dispatching the members of the school swim team one by one.

13 Stitches

Gordon assembles an unlikely team to protect Gotham from Eduardo Dorrance and his Delta Force, and Barbara reveals shocking news that will change Gordon's life forever. Elsewhere, Selina and Penguin team up to outsmart fellow villain Magpie.

Pena Dura

A military task force is called in to provide relief to Gotham, and Nygma looks for answers from Penguin, who leads him back to Hugo Strange. Meanwhile, Bruce is concerned about Selina's recent behaviour.
